description.narrative: A four-year Sanitation Marketing project was completed, with 184 per cent achievement. A total of 165,000 households purchased their own improved toilets through local entrepreneurs. Advocacy with government and the private sector resulted in commitments for national up-scaling for sanitation marketing and reduced the number of persons at risk of arsenic contaminated water to zero. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
